(laughter)

00:21:19.645 --> 00:21:20.946 line:95%,end
JILL: ...we saw it and thought of you.

00:21:21.513 --> 00:21:24.316 line:95%,end
ABBY: Ooh.

00:21:24.950 --> 00:21:25.784 line:95%,end
Pretty.

00:21:25.851 --> 00:21:27.919 line:95%,end
