I just feel you guys would be so happy
if you were someplace

00:23:02.314 --> 00:23:04.049 line:95%,end
where you had a good leader.

00:23:08.353 --> 00:23:09.821 line:95%,end
I don't think there's
anything wrong with that.

00:23:09.888 --> 00:23:12.290 line:95%,end
How many fights have you had
with her already?

00:23:12.357 --> 00:23:13.925 line:95%,end
KELLY: Oh, God, I don't even know.

00:23:14.826 --> 00:23:18.230 line:95%,end
It seems like it's a negative
