00:23:39.050 --> 00:23:40.552 line:95%,end
ABBY: <i>When we got off of the bus,</i>

00:23:40.619 --> 00:23:42.988 line:5%,start
I told my girls and their mothers,

00:23:43.054 --> 00:23:44.823 line:5%,start
game faces on.

