00:24:15.287 --> 00:24:16.221 line:95%,end
GIRL: Hi.

00:24:16.288 --> 00:24:17.389 line:95%,end
Come on. Let's go girls.

00:24:17.456 --> 00:24:19.791 line:95%,end
-All right. Good to see you.
