00:24:44.182 --> 00:24:45.584 line:95%,end
JILL: <i>Kendall's a competitor,</i>

00:24:45.650 --> 00:24:47.586 line:95%,end
<i>but I'm not sure she fully understands</i>

00:24:47.652 --> 00:24:49.054 line:5%,start
what's at stake here.

00:24:49.120 --> 00:24:51.056 line:95%,end
ABBY: Kendall, this is about you

00:24:51.122 --> 00:24:52.991 line:95%,end
