League Dance Company jacket

00:24:53.058 --> 00:24:55.494 line:95%,end
or going back to the regular process.

00:24:55.560 --> 00:24:56.561 line:95%,end
You understand?

00:24:57.062 --> 00:24:58.597 line:95%,end
Yes, mom? You understand that?

00:24:58.663 --> 00:24:59.531 line:95%,end
-JILL: I do.
