her days are numbered.

00:25:14.079 --> 00:25:15.547 line:95%,end
KELLY: Ready for a snood?

00:25:15.614 --> 00:25:16.815 line:95%,end
HOLLY: And what about that?

00:25:18.617 --> 00:25:20.652 line:95%,end
Let me go over this whole hair thing.

00:25:20.719 --> 00:25:22.587 line:95%,end
HOLLY: <i>I think the most stressful part</i>

00:25:22.654 --> 00:25:25.490 line:95%,end
