for the competition is the hair.

00:25:25.557 --> 00:25:29.628 line:5%,start
If your snood or your rat
comes undone on stage,

00:25:29.694 --> 00:25:31.263 line:5%,start
that is not going to be good.

00:25:34.566 --> 00:25:35.967 line:95%,end
ABBY: Wait a minute, wait a minute here.

00:25:36.034 --> 00:25:37.869 line:95%,end
-This is a snood.
-I know.

00:25:37.936 --> 00:25:40.705 line:95%,end
