00:25:42.607 --> 00:25:44.209 line:95%,end
You know, these moms
may not know the difference

00:25:44.276 --> 00:25:46.745 line:95%,end
between snoods, but I can tell.

00:25:46.811 --> 00:25:49.381 line:95%,end
