has to be exactly the same.

00:25:56.254 --> 00:25:58.623 line:95%,end
<i>Details could make or break a number.</i>

00:25:58.690 --> 00:26:00.625 line:95%,end
But why didn't you buy
seven new ones of that?

00:26:01.192 --> 00:26:03.929 line:95%,end
HOLLY: Because when I left
yesterday morning,

00:26:03.995 --> 00:26:07.265 line:95%,end
