don't buy something different."

00:26:11.937 --> 00:26:12.904 line:95%,end
Where you? Where were you?

00:26:12.971 --> 00:26:13.905 line:95%,end
Four different stores,

00:26:13.972 --> 00:26:15.674 line:95%,end
four different stores,
four different stores.

00:26:15.740 --> 00:26:19.544 line:95%,end
